cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.NE 

The paper discusses machine learning and deep learning models, which are commonly studied in the sub-categories of cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The focus of the paper is on interpretability, which is also a topic of interest in the sub-categories of cs.CV (Computer Vision) and cs.CL (Computation and Language). Additionally, the paper proposes modifications to LIME, which is a popular method in the sub-category of cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
